Beijing Xiao Tang Shan Hospital is being reconstructed and, if necessary, replenished with focused pneumonia: There may be ongoing human-to-human transmission, and Wuhan city chief has called for reduced staff mobility. This article must not be reprinted without written authorization from the Beijing News.
